HEADWORD: Chartless
<hw>Chart"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Without a chart;
having no guide.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not mapped; uncharted; vague.</def>
<rj><au>Barlow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

